                    <span>This is the best general AI book I've seen this far. It introduces all the popular branches of AI clearly. If you are serious about AI, you should own this book...</span>
                  
                    <div class="CustomerReviewSummary">LISP and Prolog all in one</div>
                    <div>
                      <span class="ItemCaption">Rating: </span>
